                                <support><p>Quadrangular block of stone, damaged around the edges but essentially intact; parts of the face still covered with stucco.</p>
                                    <material ana="#material.stone.limestone" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html">limestone</material>
